 INTRODUCTION
 ------------

 Details of each feature can be found in more detail in the 'DETAILS' subheading, but the program will include:
     -> photo syncing (potentially using RSync)
     -> movie database, including the ability to download files dirctly from Google Drive for offline watching
     -> music database (may become redundant due to Apple Music)
     -> browser movie streaming (could be problematic due to AWS data limits)

